Day Raider			KEY:Kobold ~ Day Raider			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.Kobold Racial Trait.SpecialQuality.Special Quality			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Day Raider],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Kobold_ReplaceVision=True,Kobold_ReplaceWeakness=True]	DESC:You're one of the few kobolds born with a greater tolerance for sunlight. You don't have light sensitivity, and you have low-light vision instead of darkvision.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Day Raider																																																																																																																														VISION:Low-Light Vision	COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.7																	FACT:Kobold_ReplaceVision|True	FACT:Kobold_ReplaceWeakness|True
Dragonmaw			KEY:Kobold ~ Dragonmaw			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.Kobold Racial Trait.SpecialAttack.Special Attack			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Dragonmaw],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Kobold_ReplaceArmor=True]						DESC:Your draconic heritage makes you smile--not just because it makes you happy, but also because your powerful jaws and teeth are proof of your kinship to a chromatic dragon. You gain a bite attack that deals 1d4 points of damage. Once per day, you can deal 1d6 points of additional energy damage with your bite attack. The damage type depends on your scale color: acid damage for black or green, electricity for blue, fire for red, or cold for white. If you have a different scale color, you still gain the bite attack, but can't do the additional energy damage.	DESC:This racial trait replaces the armor racial trait.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Dragonmaw			MULT:YES	CHOOSE:ABILITYSELECTION|Kobold Scale Color|QUALIFIED	ABILITY:Kobold Scale Color|AUTOMATIC|%LIST	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Bite	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Dragonmaw Bite Type|1																				COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.7	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|1								FACT:Kobold_ReplaceArmor|True
Echo Whistler		KEY:Kobold ~ Echo Whistler		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.Kobold Racial Trait.SpecialQuality.Special Quality			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Echo Whistler],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Kobold_ReplaceCrafty=True]					DESC:By observing the noises in underground tunnels, you learned to uncannily mimic any voice or sound you heard. Three times per day, you can attempt to trick someone in this way by making a Bluff check against the listener's Sense Motive check. You get a +2 circumstance bonus on this check if you're in tunnels or other structures where your voice can echo.	DESC:This racial trait replaces crafty.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Echo Whistler																																																																																										COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.7	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|3								FACT:Kobold_ReplaceCrafty|True
Frightener			KEY:Kobold ~ Frightener			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.Kobold Racial Trait.SpecialQuality.Special Quality			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Frightener],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Kobold_ReplaceArmor=True]						DESC:Like the great dragons, you can strike fear in the hearts of your foes with your majestic presence. Few enemies suspect that you make yourself look more dangerous with simple tricks you learned back when you were newly hatched. You gain a +1 racial bonus to the DC of saving throws against spells you cast with the fear descriptor.	DESC:This racial trait replaces the armor racial trait.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Frightener																																																																								BONUS:DC|DESCRIPTOR.Fear|1															COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.7																	FACT:Kobold_ReplaceArmor|True
Prehensile Tail		KEY:Kobold ~ Prehensile Tail		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.Kobold Racial Trait.SpecialQuality.Special Quality.Applied Bonus	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Prehensile Tail],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Kobold_ReplaceArmor=True]					DESC:Your tail is especially flexible and strong, so you've learned to use it for both movement and simple tricks. You gain a +2 racial bonus on Acrobatics and Climb checks, and you can use your tail to draw a hidden weapon as a move action instead of as a standard action.	DESC:This racial trait replaces the armor racial trait.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Prehensile Tail																																																																																								BONUS:SKILL|Acrobatics,Climb|2|TYPE=Racial							COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.7	ASPECT:RacialSkillModifier|+2 Acrobatics, +2 Climb								FACT:Kobold_ReplaceArmor|True
Secret Strider		KEY:Kobold ~ Secret Strider		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.Kobold Racial Trait.SpecialQuality.Special Quality			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Secret Strider],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Kobold_ReplaceCrafty=True]					DESC:You have the ability to traverse the wilderness without a trace. Twice per day, you can move through natural surroundings without leaving a trail for 1 minute, increasing the DC of any attempts to track you by 10.	DESC:This racial trait replaces crafty.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Secret Strider																																																																																																																	COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.7	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day	ASPECT:CheckCount|2								FACT:Kobold_ReplaceCrafty|True
Shoulder to Shoulder	KEY:Kobold ~ Shoulder to Shoulder	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.Kobold Racial Trait.SpecialQuality.Special Quality			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Shoulder to Shoulder],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Kobold_ReplaceCrafty=True]				DESC:Having lived and worked in close quarters with your tribe-mates, you've learned how to maneuver within their personal space without disturbing them. You can occupy the same space as one other Small ally without penalty. If you share a space with another kobold who has this trait, you each gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC, as you help jostle one another out of the way of incoming attacks. You also gain a +1 racial bonus on aid another rolls.	DESC:This racial trait replaces crafty.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Shoulder to Shoulder																																																																									COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.7																	FACT:Kobold_ReplaceCrafty|True
Spellcaster Sneak		KEY:Kobold ~ Spellcaster Sneak	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.Kobold Racial Trait.SpecialQuality.Special Quality			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Spellcaster Sneak],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Kobold_ReplaceCrafty=True]					DESC:Traversing the tunnels near big, nasty, hungry creatures, you learned to keep quiet--and to keep your spells quiet too. You gain a +2 racial bonus on Stealth checks, and once per day you can gain the benefit of the Silent Spell feat on a spell you cast.	DESC:This racial trait replaces crafty.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Spellcaster Sneak																																																																																												BONUS:SKILL|Stealth|2|TYPE=Racial									COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.7	ASPECT:RacialSkillModifier|+2 Stealth	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|1	FACT:Kobold_ReplaceCrafty|True
Wild Forest Kobold	KEY:Kobold ~ Wild Forest Kobold	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.Kobold Racial Trait.SpecialQuality.Special Quality			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Wild Forest Kobold],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Kobold_ReplaceCrafty=True]				DESC:You're one of the barbaric kobolds dwelling in the forests of the surface world. Your culture shuns artifice, but teaches how to endure and hunt. You gain a +2 racial bonus on Perception and Survival checks.	DESC:This racial trait replaces crafty.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Wild Forest Kobold	DESC:Stealth and Survival are always class skills for you.																																																																ABILITY:Class Skill|AUTOMATIC|Stealth|Survival																			BONUS:SKILL|Perception,Survival|2|TYPE=Racial							COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.7	ASPECT:RacialSkillModifier|+2 Perception, +2 Survival								FACT:Kobold_ReplaceCrafty|True
Wyrmcrowned			KEY:Kobold ~ Wyrmcrowned		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.Kobold Racial Trait.SpecialQuality.Special Quality			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Wyrmcrowned],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Kobold_ReplaceCrafty=True]						DESC:Your horns have grown to the extent that they appear similar to those of a dragon who shares your scale color, lending a draconic power or menace to your dealings with others. Choose either Diplomacy or Intimidate. You gain a +2 racial bonus on checks with that skill, and it is always a class skill for you.	DESC:This racial trait replaces crafty.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kobold ~ Wyrmcrowned																																													STACK:NO	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NUMCHOICES=1|SKILL|Diplomacy|Intimidate																												BONUS:SKILL|LIST|2|TYPE=Racial			CSKILL:LIST					COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.7	ASPECT:RacialSkillModifier|+2 %1|%LIST										FACT:Kobold_ReplaceCrafty|True

